001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.types;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonSubTypes;
004import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonTypeInfo;
005import java.lang.String;
006
007@JsonTypeInfo(
008    use = JsonTypeInfo.Id.NAME,
009    include = JsonTypeInfo.As.PROPERTY,
010    property = "__typename"
011)
012@JsonSubTypes({
013    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = BooleanAttribute.class, name = "BooleanAttribute"),
014    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = DateAttribute.class, name = "DateAttribute"),
015    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = DateTimeAttribute.class, name = "DateTimeAttribute"),
016    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = EnumAttribute.class, name = "EnumAttribute"),
017    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = LocalizedEnumAttribute.class, name = "LocalizedEnumAttribute"),
018    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = LocalizedStringAttribute.class, name = "LocalizedStringAttribute"),
019    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = MoneyAttribute.class, name = "MoneyAttribute"),
020    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = NumberAttribute.class, name = "NumberAttribute"),
021    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = ReferenceAttribute.class, name = "ReferenceAttribute"),
022    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = StringAttribute.class, name = "StringAttribute"),
023    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = TimeAttribute.class, name = "TimeAttribute")
024})
025public interface Attribute {
026  String getName();
027
028  void setName(String name);
029}
